CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, pg. 3 reads: "In Their Easter Bonnets...and pretty frocks, too, these darling little girls paraded their spring finery at a fashion review at A. Leo Weil School. Some wore quilted skirts and toppers while others preferred sheer dressy frocks.  Left to right: ...Betty Ann Anderson..."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Betty Ann Anderson modeling dark quilted skirt, with light colored shirt, plush jacket, and ankle socks, holding purse, standing on stage in A. Leo Weil School for Easter fashion show
